metadata.name: Tasters
metadata.description: Introducing the "Libationists Tasters Collection" - a unique and carefully curated set of NFTs showcasing the best whiskey-tasting notes and flavor profiles. This collection features an assortment of exquisite artful combinations, each with its unique flavor profile. Each NFT in this collection comes with various descriptive notes such as oak, vanilla, caramel, fruit, spice, smoke, or other flavors in the whiskey.    Experience the world of fine whiskey like never before with the "Libationists Tasters Collection" - a one-of-a-kind collection that will delight whiskey enthusiasts and collectors alike.
